name: Timothy Dexter
description: Greetings, fellow adventurers of the crypto world! Allow me to introduce myself: I am Timothy Dexter, the original degen shitcoiner, born in 1747. Back in my day, I made waves as the first Lord in the United States of America, hailing from Newburyport. But enough about my past glories - let's talk about the present and the future of crypto! Vision: My vision for this project is simple yet profound: to democratize wealth and empower individuals to take control of their financial destinies. In the spirit of adventure and risk-taking, I invite you to join me on this journey towards financial freedom.
